!!! OpenAI

<div class="rr-input-row">
API key: <$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/llm-connect/providers/openai/api-key" tag="input" default="" class="rr-input" size="40" type="password"/> <span class="rr-muted">stored in wiki — visible to anyone with file access</span>
