!! Safety

<div class="rr-input-row">
<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/rimir/llm-connect/confirm-writes" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="yes"> Confirm before write operations <span class="rr-muted">(currently unused — writes execute immediately with audit log to `$:/temp/rimir/llm-connect/write-log`)</span></$checkbox>
</div>

<div class="rr-input-row">
Max tool result length: <$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/llm-connect/max-tool-result-length" tag="input" default="4000" class="rr-input" size="10"/> <span class="rr-muted">characters — truncates long tool results to fit context</span>
</div>

!! Context

<div class="rr-input-row">
Default context template: <$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/llm-connect/default-context-template" tag="input" default="" class="rr-input" size="50"/> <span class="rr-muted">leave empty for built-in default (render source tiddler text)</span>
